---
import SiteLayout from "@layouts/SiteLayout.astro"
import Card from "@components/Card.astro"
import EditLink from "@components/EditLink.astro"
---

<SiteLayout>
	<main class="px-3 lg:px-0">
		<div class="mt-9 prose mb-6">
			<h3>What's the goddamn point?</h3>
			<p><em>Of course</em> there's a depression epidemic. At some level, we all realize that we're wasting our lives
				in bullshit jobs, doing what we're told so the rich may grow richer.</p>
			<p>But what other choice do we have?</p>
		</div>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid mt-6 mb-8">
			<Card href="/a-viable-alternative" title="A viable alternative">
				<p>A share of this planet's land and natural wealth is your birthright.</p>
				<p>Nobody should be forced to pay rent for their right to existence, and here's why in the future, nobody
					will.</p>
			</Card>
		</ul>
		<div class="my-6 bg-gray-100 h-[2px]" />
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid my-8">
			<Card href="/sustainable-or-sustained" title="Sustained? Or just sustainable?"
				body="What happens to a physical thing when its owner no longer needs it?" />
			<Card href="/things-that-recycle-themselves" title="Things that recycle themselves"
				body="What if every material was a recycled material â€“ all without any effort on your part?" />
			<Card href="/where-profits-go" title="Where do the profits go?"
				body="A thing costs more than its material. Where does the rest of the bill go?" />
			<Card href="/renewable-money" title="Renewable money"
				body="If you've paid the fair price, how can you ensure that the producer will pay it forward?" />
			<Card href="/who-can-afford-to-care" title="Who can afford to care?"
				body="Many of us can barely afford existing prices. Who could possibly pay fair prices?" />
			<Card href="/transferably-certifiably-green" title="Transferably, certifiably, green"
				body="What if an investment in our collective future could be an investment in your financial future?" />
		</ul>
		<div class="my-6 bg-gray-100 h-[2px]" />
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid my-8">
			<Card href="/your-share" title="What's your share?"
				body="Earth has a lot of space, but it also has a lot of people. If we split things evenly between us, how much do we each get?" />
			<Card href="/" title="Who owns your share?" body="" />
			<Card href="/" title="What do we consume?" body="" />
			<Card href="/" title="What could you produce?" body="" />
		</ul>
	</main>
	<footer class="text-center text-sm text-gray-400 underline border-t-2 border-gray-100 p-4 mt-12">
		<EditLink fileURL={import.meta.url} />
	</footer>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		max-width: 70ch;
	}

	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(30ch, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>